This is the code for a version of the prototype that uses 4 gloves and for the Lemonade song. 
I haven't yet put in the tilt sensor, nor the shoulder/thigh pads. 

I will have to upload a hi-res photo of the board to clarify pin configuration. 

This project is a work in progress and future versions will be documented. 

There is the regular controller code, as well as the callibration code, which I use to callibrate the unique voltage ID's for each glove.
This is to ensure that each glove is read correctly when running through the filter function. 
I will add the callibration code soon.
